<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="bhw24May1938"><font color="red">24 May 1938</font> <i>NLHW</i> (from Harriet Weaver to Paul L&eacute;on): Please give my thanks to Mr Joyce for the further manuscript pages enclosed in your letter. I am sorry to hear that Mr Joyce has had a rather acute eye attack since his return from Zurich. </div>
